Saṃyutta Nikāya 25 
1. Cakkhuvagga 
8. Rūpataṇhāsutta 
Sāvatthinidānaṃ. 
“Rūpataṇhā, bhikkhave, aniccā vipariṇāmī aññathābhāvī; 
saddataṇhā … 
gandhataṇhā … 
rasataṇhā … 
phoṭṭhabbataṇhā … 
dhammataṇhā aniccā vipariṇāmī aññathābhāvī. 
Yo, bhikkhave, ime dhamme evaṃ saddahati adhimuccati, ayaṃ vuccati ‘saddhānusārī … pe … 
sambodhiparāyano’”ti. 
Aṭṭhamaṃ. 
